---
import Layout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="How we test Â· Rocky Mountain Smoking"
  description="Our testing, measurement, and update rules for altitude-first BBQ recipes and techniques."
>
  <main class="bg-[var(--color-page)] py-14 text-[var(--color-text)] sm:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl space-y-10 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <header class="space-y-3">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[var(--color-muted)]">Trust</p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] sm:text-4xl">How we test</h1>
        <p class="max-w-3xl text-lg text-[var(--color-muted)] sm:text-xl">
          Every recipe and technique is built on logged cooks, temperature notes, and explicit altitude adjustments.
          We want you to see the work behind the smoke.
        </p>
      </header>

      <section class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200/70 bg-white/90 p-6 shadow-[0_18px_40px_-35px_rgba(0,0,0,0.6)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)]">What we log</h2>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-3 text-[var(--color-muted)]">
            <li>Pit temp, internal temp, and time-to-target for every cook.</li>
            <li>Fuel and wood usage by weight or split count.</li>
            <li>Altitude, humidity, and wind notes for each session.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200/70 bg-white/90 p-6 shadow-[0_18px_40px_-35px_rgba(0,0,0,0.6)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)]">How we verify</h2>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-3 text-[var(--color-muted)]">
            <li>Repeat cooks with the same target temps.</li>
            <li>Side-by-side adjustments to isolate altitude effects.</li>
            <li>Taste and texture checks after full rest windows.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200/70 bg-white/90 p-6 shadow-[0_18px_40px_-35px_rgba(0,0,0,0.6)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)]">Updates and corrections</h2>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-3 text-[var(--color-muted)]">
            <li>Each post lists a published date; material updates get a visible note.</li>
            <li>If a method changes after retesting, we rewrite the section and log the change.</li>
            <li>Send notes to <a class="underline hover:text-[var(--color-text)]" href="mailto:editor@rockymountainsmoking.com">editor@rockymountainsmoking.com</a>.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200/70 bg-white/90 p-6 shadow-[0_18px_40px_-35px_rgba(0,0,0,0.6)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)]">Editorial guardrails</h2>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-3 text-[var(--color-muted)]">
            <li>No folklore without testing; measurement beats legend.</li>
            <li>Clear ingredient and temperature callouts in every recipe.</li>
            <li>No hidden sponsorships; affiliate links are disclosed.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
